</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-148D173E-3D71-4FD7-86B0-AF3518B8E22D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6C94B7A3-1EB0-4E0B-AFCC-378AC6E6D562-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6C94B7A3-1EB0-4E0B-AFCC-378AC6E6D562-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-8CF65E4E-5321-4108-97B0-C3E452D8EF53" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3052A4CE-DB7D-400D-B5E0-0E92BE46EFA6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3052A4CE-DB7D-400D-B5E0-0E92BE46EFA6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
